## ⚠️ Open Items (Blockers for Warfighter Pilot)

- **CAC/PIV Auth:** Current Supabase Auth is appropriate for OEM commercial product. Warfighter use case may require CAC/PIV integration, SSO with DoD identity providers, or IL-compliant auth flows. Must be scoped before warfighter pilot begins.
- **Cached Data Policies:** Not yet defined. Must be resolved before warfighter pilot begins.
